This repository consists of several example of how to connect Flash Player/AIR to Arduino hardware.  The examples are used in an Adobe TV series on this particular subject.  The various sensors included, and their corresponding videos are:

Getting Started
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tAHjq-mJqp0

Connecting to Adobe Flash
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ogSvvYSdews

Accelerometer
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yIX-_wDStgI

Passive Infrared (PIR)
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gsFQ3OZojBk

Photocells
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LJe8dhvmjeo

RGB LED
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_YcLwpsAlAo

Temperature and Humidity
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EyzKsejOsPs

Ultrasonic Range Finder
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VXie_PE-T4c

XBee Wireless
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9VfiyDBjegs